---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import heroImg from '../assets/img/about/hero-capoeira.jpg';
---

<Layout
  title="About Dendê Arts | Capoeira Community"
  description="Learn about Dendê Arts, founded by Chris 'Calado' Rodriguez. Discover our mission to grow the Capoeira community for all ages and skill levels."
>
  <div class="about-page">
    <div class="main-grid">
      <Nav />
    </div>

    <div class="about-hero-wrapper">
      <Image
        src={heroImg}
        alt="A group of capoeira practitioners performing a synchronized movement in a vibrant outdoor setting"
        class="about-hero-img"
        width={1087}
        height={505}
      />
    </div>

    <section class="about-content-section">
      <div class="about-inner">
        <h1 class="about-heading">About Dendê Arts</h1>

        <div class="about-vision-mission">
          <div class="about-col">
            <h2 class="about-col-title">The vision</h2>
            <p>Capoeira is more than flips and kicks – it's about connection, creativity, and self-expression. At Calado A Dende Arts, we're breaking down barriers to make this incredible art form accessible to all ages, all skill levels, and all walks of life.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-col">
            <h2 class="about-col-title">The mission</h2>
            <p>At Dende Arts, our mission is to grow the Capoeira community and enhance the experience for practitioners of all levels. We believe that Capoeira is more than just a martial art – it's a way of life that fosters physical fitness, mental resilience, and cultural appreciation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-calado-section">
      <div class="about-inner">
        <h3 class="about-calado-title">Meet Calado: Your Guide to Capoeira</h3>

        <div class="about-bio">
          <p>Dendê Arts was founded in New Jersey by Chris "Calado" Rodriguez. A passionate Capoeira teacher, web developer, and social media power-house. Since 2007, Calado has dedicated himself to the art of Capoeira.</p>

          <p>Calado's training started in High School when his cousin invited him to a Brazilian martial arts class. In 2012 Calado started training with Mestre Cebolinha former of Cordão de Ouro. This creative and dynamic style – a combination of Regional and Angola is the hallmark of Calado's style. He also learned from great teachers like Professor Rob Grey, Dr. Andrea Spina, and Mestre Cueca.</p>

          <p>In 2016, Calado started teaching in California at the Google Complex in Mountainview. A year later he moved back to the East Coast and started teaching in Astoria, New York City and later he began teaching classes in Newark, NJ.</p>

          <p>Calado's teaching methodology is a combination of traditional Capoeira training methods and modern skills training. The traditions learned from incredible talents like Mestres Xuxo, Cueca, João Grande, Brasilia, Cebolinha, Cabelo, and many more.</p>

          <p>Calado knows what it's like to juggle work, life, and passion. That's why he built Dendê Arts as a way to integrate the joy of learning and doing Capoeira into your daily routine.</p>

          <p>Calado's innovative approach includes:</p>

          <ul class="about-list">
            <li><strong>Online Resources:</strong> A wealth of tutorials, tips, and insights available through his blog, YouTube channel, and social media platforms.</li>
            <li><strong>In-Person Classes:</strong> Hands-on training sessions designed to help students master the art of Capoeira in a supportive environment.</li>
            <li><strong>Capoeira Gear:</strong> High-quality, handcrafted equipment to enhance your practice and performance.</li>
            <li><strong>Community Building:</strong> A commitment to fostering connections among Capoeira enthusiasts, creating a global network of like-minded individuals.</li>
          </ul>

          <p>Calado's vision is that more people learn the joy of Capoeira. The joy of moving, flipping, kicking, playing music, and interacting with a global community.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-cta-section">
      <div class="about-cta-inner">
        <h2 class="about-cta-heading">Ready to start a new chapter in your capoeira journey?</h2>
        <a href="/abada-joggers" class="btn about-cta-btn">Shop Abadas Today!</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    background-color: #d2eaef;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .about-hero-wrapper {
    max-width: 1087px;
    margin: 3rem auto 0;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-hero-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: block;
    aspect-ratio: 1087 / 505;
  }

  .about-content-section {
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-inner {
    max-width: 956px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-heading {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 3.625rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.21;
    letter-spacing: -0.06rem;
    color: #1d221b;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about-vision-mission {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  @media (min-width: 700px) {
    .about-vision-mission {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
  }

  .about-col-title {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 2rem;
    color: #1d221b;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .about-col p {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.75rem;
    color: #1d221b;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-calado-section {
    padding: 0 1.5rem 4rem;
  }

  .about-calado-title {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 2.625rem;
    color: #1d221b;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-bio p {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.75rem;
    color: #1d221b;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-list {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.75rem;
    color: #1d221b;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-list li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-cta-section {
    background-color: white;
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-cta-inner {
    max-width: 1090px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .about-cta-heading {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.625rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 3.25rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.025rem;
    color: #434343;
    max-width: 580px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-cta-btn {
    background-color: #0f8095;
    color: white;
    border-radius: 30px;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
    white-space: nowrap;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .about-cta-btn:hover {
    background-color: #0a6b7d;
  }
</style>
